{"id":232668201,"title":"生活隨筆 #3 大阪燒體驗","content":"前情提要：打工處年底有個忘年會，老闆娘說要在那之前教會我幾道料理，那天要讓我當大廚😂\n\n—————————\n\n今晚剛好有個人數稍多的活動，老闆娘說是個練習手藝的好機會，叫我今天學會怎麼煎大阪燒。\n\n愛好大阪燒的我吃過各種大阪燒，但就是沒有自己煎過，所以感覺很新鮮特別有幹勁😂\n（想當初章魚燒也是在打工處學會的🤔\n\n從攪麵粉到下鍋到煎好，這樣的動作大概重複了不下20次。明明是冬天但卻煎到汗流浹背，上了電車鼻子裡還是大阪燒的味道😅\n\nhttps://i.imgur.com/7Di6oYx.jpg\n\n雖然很累但聽到客人說好吃好吃就覺得很有成就感。也才知道，一句ご馳走さまです真的能讓做菜的人感到很開心😆\n\nhttps://i.imgur.com/yBoZDCU.jpg\n\n煎了20幾個也有點心得了！\n忘年會完差不多可以出師了吧😉","excerpt":"前情提要：打工處年底有個忘年會，老闆娘說要在那之前教會我幾道料理，那天要讓我當大廚，—————————，今晚剛好有個人數稍多的活動，老闆娘說是個練習手藝的好機會，叫我今天學會怎麼煎大阪燒。愛好大阪燒的","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"ee51d6cd-ad7e-4d73-b79a-3ce32ea7798b","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-11T14:38:46.872Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-11T14:38:46.872Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":16,"tags":[],"topics":["日本生活","日本打工","大阪燒"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"日本生活","forumAlias":"japan_life","school":"我是住在東京的大學生","department":"kaiw_inut","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":16}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/7Di6oYx.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/yBoZDCU.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"38f85caa-e370-4ec7-bc0c-507595d10f2d","url":"https://i.imgur.com/7Di6oYxl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/7Di6oYxl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/7Di6oYxl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-11T14:38:46.872Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-11T14:38:46.872Z"},{"id":"38f85caa-e370-4ec7-bc0c-507595d10f2d","url":"https://i.imgur.com/7Di6oYx.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/7Di6oYx","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/7Di6oYxl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-11T14:38:46.872Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-